<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Confirme ton compte StudyLink</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#0f172a;font-family:'Inter',Arial,sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#0f172a;padding:40px 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#1e293b;border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">

          <%# Header %>
          <tr>
            <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#ec4899);padding:36px 40px;text-align:center;">
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-radius:14px;padding:12px 16px;display:inline-block;">
                    <span style="font-size:24px;">🎓</span>
                    <span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;margin-left:8px;vertical-align:middle;">StudyLink</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <%# Body %>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:40px 40px 32px;">
              <h1 style="margin:0 0 8px;color:#ffffff;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;">Bienvenue, <%= @resource.display_name %> 👋</h1>
              <p style="margin:0 0 24px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
                Ton compte StudyLink est presque prêt. Il te reste une étape : confirme ton adresse e-mail en cliquant sur le bouton ci-dessous.
              </p>

              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding:8px 0 32px;">
                    <%= link_to confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token),
                                style: "display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#8b5cf6);color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;padding:16px 40px;border-radius:14px;letter-spacing:0.01em;" do %>
                      Confirmer mon compte
                    <% end %>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:24px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 4px;color:#64748b;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">Le lien ne fonctionne pas ?</p>
                <p style="margin:0;color:#94a3b8;font-size:13px;word-break:break-all;">
                  Copie et colle cette URL dans ton navigateur :<br>
                  <span style="color:#6366f1;"><%= confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %></span>
                </p>
              </div>

              <p style="margin:0;color:#475569;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;">
                Si tu n'es pas à l'origine de cette inscription, tu peux ignorer cet e-mail. Aucune action ne sera effectuée.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <%# Footer %>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px 40px 32px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
              <p style="margin:0;color:#334155;font-size:12px;text-align:center;">
                © <%= Date.current.year %> StudyLink — La plateforme d'entraide étudiante<br>
                Cet e-mail a été envoyé à <strong style="color:#475569;"><%= @resource.email %></strong>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
